sudospaces.com/senvietdecor/2020/03/00c7c43476f38fadd6e2-750x563.jpg\" width=\"750\" /><figcaption>Hình ảnh khung nhà thờ họ 5 gian 8 mái gõ pachy</figcaption></figure><p>&nbsp;</p><figure id=\"attachment_11248\"><img alt=\"hinh-anh-thiet-ke-thi-cong-nha-go-cau-kien-cham-tro \" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" data-src=\"https://sudospaces.com/senvietdecor/2020/03/z1767749831145_d6aedf792c2896b20ca3d77d3eac421a-750x563.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://sudospaces.com/senvietdecor/2020/03/z1767749831145_d6aedf792c2896b20ca3d77d3eac421a-750x563.jpg 750w, https://sudospaces.com/senvietdecor/2020/03/z1767749831145_d6aedf792c2896b20ca3d77d3eac421a-250x188.jpg 250w, https://sudospaces.com/senvietdecor/2020/03/z1767749831145_d6aedf792c2896b20ca3d77d3eac421a-768x576.jpg 768w\" height=\"563\" src=\"https://sudospaces.com/senvietdecor/2020/03/z1767749831145_d6aedf792c2896b20ca3d77d3eac421a-750x563.jpg\" width=\"750\" /><figcaption>Các cấu kiện chạm trổ sắc nét nổi bật</figcaption></figure><figure id=\"attachment_11254\"><img alt=\"hinh-anh-thiet-ke-thi-cong-nha-go-nha-tho-ho-lop-mai\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" data-src=\"https://sudospaces.com/senvietdecor/2020/03/z1668658260437_8f9318372b9d57971e29372bc5b63ca7-1-750x563.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://sudospaces.com/senvietdecor/2020/03/z1668658260437_8f9318372b9d57971e29372bc5b63ca7-1-750x563.jpg 750w, https://sudospaces.com/senvietdecor/2020/03/z1668658260437_8f9318372b9d57971e29372bc5b63ca7-1-250x188.jpg 250w, https://sudospaces.com/senvietdecor/2020/03/z1668658260437_8f9318372b9d57971e29372bc5b63ca7-1-768x576.jpg 768w\" height=\"563\" src=\"https://sudospaces.com/senvietdecor/2020/03/z1668658260437_8f9318372b9d57971e29372bc5b63ca7-1-750x563.jpg\" width=\"750\" /><figcaption>Nhà gỗ 5 gian 8 mái giai đoạn lợp mái</figcaption></figure><figure id=\"attachment_11268\"><figcaption>Hình ảnh hoàn thiện lắp đặt nội thất</figcaption></figure><p>Toàn cảnh nội thất phòng thờ:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>